IsWorkingDay = 
SWITCH(
    TRUE(),
    WEEKDAY('Calendar'[Date], 2) > 5, "Not a Working Day", -- Weekends (Saturday and Sunday)
    "Working Day"
)


Explanation:
WEEKDAY([Date], 2): Returns the days from date as a number where Monday = 1 and Sunday = 7.
> 5: Identifies weekends (Saturday-6 and Sunday-7).
"Not a Working Day": Label for weekends. //can be customized
"Working Day": Default label for other days. //can be customized
